      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Book book)
        This method compares an instance of this Book, with another instance of Book. It should not consider genres.

        Algorithm:
        1. Compare titles 2. If titles are the same, compare authors 3. If authors are the same, take the difference in years

        Parameters:
        book - The book to which we are comparing this instance of Book
        Returns:
        A negative, zero, or positive integer depending on whether this belongs before, at the same place, or after the book being compared to
